description: If it’s feeling a little too lava-hot out in Las Vegas, Frankie’s Ice Cream Truck has got just the refreshing treat for you. This family-run truck is serving up a delightful selection of sweet noshes, like novelty popsicles, handmade banana splits, brownie sundaes, waffle cones, and milkshakes too. And if you’re feeling hungry for something savory, Frankie’s is your one-stop-shop. Just step on up and order some ballpark nachos, hot dogs, or delicious roasted Mexican street corn (elotes). And if you’re planning a birthday party or big event, Frankie’s Ice Cream Truck, with all its fun and frills, is frankly the perfect choice.
name: Frankie's Ice Cream Truck
